list.s: Jack looks at the toe, bites off part of the nail to trim it
the dress sweeps over a lantern, knocking it over and part of the deck ignites
Will is tossed into a lower part of the deck, partially filled with water
Wyvern, who is part of the wall, breaks his head away from the wall, leaving his brains behind
Norrington and Will resume their part of the rooftop duel
